public class AdapterSettings
extends Object
    AdapterSettings

    AdapterSettings: General settings for any Adapter, to be specified when instantiating the Adapter.Implement this class to make your own Toolkit settings, e.g. SpeckleAdapterSettings.

      • getOnlyUpdateChangedObjects

        public Boolean getOnlyUpdateChangedObjects()
        If true, Objects found to be the same according to the AdapterComparer for the provided type are checked for full equality using the HashComparer of the type (which by default checks every property except BHoM_Guid). If equal according to the HashComparer, they are not updated. Otherwise, Objects found identical according to the AdapterComparer for the provided type are sent to the Update method. (Required)

      • setOnlyUpdateChangedObjects

        public void setOnlyUpdateChangedObjects​(Boolean onlyUpdateChangedObjects)
        If true, Objects found to be the same according to the AdapterComparer for the provided type are checked for full equality using the HashComparer of the type (which by default checks every property except BHoM_Guid). If equal according to the HashComparer, they are not updated. Otherwise, Objects found identical according to the AdapterComparer for the provided type are sent to the Update method. (Required)
